n passer til mat. Han har diplom p\u00e5 at han har Norges beste Riesling-vinkart, kanskje er det et av verdens beste ogs\u00e5.", "Og n\u00e5 kan han snart ogs\u00e5 servere sin egen Riesling-vin - s\u00e5 kom ikke her!"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "kultur|vin"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "b4e10c9ada3e6a874f00aefb4d4dfb0a2d45a0064323fdf7754c8e431c6455ab"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-06-30T21:15:22.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Restauranteieren og Riesling-fanatikeren Calle Fegth kommer med en egen Riesling-vin p\u00e5 Vinmonopolet i januar 2009."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1261937.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Credo"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/48f8cef2c4529474fa022cb344d7c413e31162dd.jpg?5956bf6a"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Calle med egen Riesling-vin -adressa.no", "Satser p\u00e5 vin", "PerFegth (perfekt)", "Gir prestisje"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "48f8cef2c4529474fa022cb344d7c413e31162dd"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["vinpuls", "vinklubb", "ulf dalheim", "vin", "database"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "vinpuls,vinklubb,ulf dalheim,vin,database"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["kultur", "vin"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "food-and-drink"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": ["michelin", "vinmonopolet"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["verdens fremste", "vin", "restaurant"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["better wines", "weingut georg breuer", "norges", "calle fegth", "winemaker", "rheingau", "calle", "oro", "haga restaurant", "schlossberg", "wine bar", "rune pal og jan bruse andersen", "boccuse", "kokopelli", "credo restaurant", "riesling perfegth", "willy", "calle feght"]}, {"field": "kw-locatio